x4freetext: Fast neutron capture cross-section measurements of
time-of-flight. Ratio of cross sections of the
unknown to the standard at a given energy obtained from
ratio of areas of the neutron-capture peaks.
Cross sections used were mean values of
experimental data,as recommended in report BNL-325,1966
Corrections were not applied for multiple scattering
